{"id":336278,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/03/冯学荣-《接受日本记者专访实录（二）》/","date":"2014-03-11T06:19:39Z","modified":"2014-03-11T06:19:39Z","title":"冯学荣 | 《接受日本记者专访实录（二）》","content":"<p><p align=\"center\">\n<span>《接受日本记者专访实录（二）》</span></p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n<span> </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n<span> </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n<span> </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n<u><span>日本记者、撰稿人田中奈美来信</span></u></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span>尊敬的冯学荣老师：</span></p>\n<p>\n<span> </span></p>\n<p>\n<span>您好！我回信晚了不好意思。我的下一步的问题如下。</span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（1）您写“日本为什么侵华”这个问题，99%的国民的答案是错误的</span><span>。</span><span>那么</span><span>他</span><span>们的答案是什么？您对他们的答案错误的背景有什么看法？</span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（2）您在香港出版时这本书也应起了强烈反响。那么香港人对日本侵华历史的看法与大陆的一样吗？香港人一般怎么看日本和中日历史？</span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（3）您出版时有没有怕挨骂？您出版后有没有人骂您说您是卖国贼什么的？如果没有的话，您有没有感觉中国人更想知道客观的历史？我想了解您从读者的反应得到的感受。</span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（4）您了解到的读者大概多大岁，有什么样的背景？</span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（5）您在书上写您写的是客观的史实。那么您对这史实有什么看法？</span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（6）您对现在的中日关系，还有日本政治和外交有什么看法吗？</span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（7）您与日本有什么关系？比如您的工作与日本有关，或者从小喜欢看日本漫画等。</span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（8）关于您的背景</span><span>。</span><span>您为何什么时候开始那么热爱历史？您现在做什么工作（与历史完全没关系的吗？</span><span>）</span><span>您的大概的年龄（60后？70后？80后？）</span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（9）下一个您在准备写的题目是什么？</span></p>\n<p>\n<span> 我的问题比较多，希望我没有妨碍您的工作和研究。能够回答范围内给我回复的话感激不尽！</span></p>\n<p>\n<span>                       </span><br />\n<span><br />\n                                           </span><span>田中奈美</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n<u><span>答记者问如下</span></u></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span>（1）您写“日本</span><span>为</span><span>什么侵</span><span>华</span><span>”</span><span>这</span><span>个</span><span>问题</span><span>，99%的国民的答案是</span><span>错误</span><span>的。那么他</span><span>们</span><span>的答案是什么？您</span><span>对</span><span>他</span><span>们</span><span>的答案</span><span>错误</span><span>的背景有什么看法？</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span>答：</span><span>中国</span><span>的国民</span><span>由于长期受书籍、影视作品的影响，</span><span>大体</span><span>对</span><span>中日</span><span>历</span><span>史</span><span>抱</span><span>有</span><span>这</span><span>样</span><span>的</span><span>观</span><span>念：“日本自从丰臣秀吉</span><span>时</span><span>代开始，就有一个“</span><span>灭</span><span>亡中国”的既定国策，然后日本人在等待了339年之后，在1937年</span><span>终</span><span>于</span><span>发现</span><span>时</span><span>机到了，于是</span><span>倾</span><span>巢出</span><span>动</span><span>、</span><span>全面</span><span>侵</span><span>华</span><span>。”</span> <span>这</span><span>个版本的故事</span><span>虽</span><span>然很精彩，但是恐怕是不符合事</span><span>实</span><span>的。中、日之</span><span>间</span><span>的</span><span>战</span><span>争，必</span><span>须</span><span>放在以下两个基本的</span><span>时</span><span>代背景之下、去挖掘其</span><span>发</span><span>生的</span><span>缘</span><span>由，否</span><span>则</span><span>就不会有准确的</span><span>认识</span><span>：1、殖民主</span><span>义</span><span>。2、共</span><span>产</span><span>主</span><span>义</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（2）您在香港出版</span><span>时这</span><span>本</span><span>书</span><span>也</span><span>应</span><span>起了</span><span>强</span><span>烈反响。那么香港人</span><span>对</span><span>日本侵</span><span>华</span><span>历</span><span>史的看法与大</span><span>陆</span><span>的一</span><span>样</span><span>吗</span><span>？香港人一般怎么看日本和中日</span><span>历</span><span>史？</span></p>\n<p><span>答：本</span><span>书</span><span>香港版本</span><span>销</span><span>售量至今大</span><span>约</span><span>4</span><span>,000本，其中至少</span><span>有</span><span>一半，是被中国大</span><span>陆</span><span>的</span><span>读</span><span>者</span><span>买</span><span>走</span><span>的。据我所知，香港人一般不关心</span><span>历</span><span>史，而关心</span><span>历</span><span>史的那</span><span>一小</span><span>部分</span><span>香港</span><span>人，</span><span>对</span><span>中日</span><span>历</span><span>史的看法，与中国大</span><span>陆</span><span>人</span><span>的看法应该</span><span>是大同小异的。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（3）您出版</span><span>时</span><span>有没有怕挨</span><span>骂</span><span>？您出版后有没有人</span><span>骂</span><span>您</span><span>说</span><span>您是</span><span>卖</span><span>国</span><span>贼</span><span>什么的？如果没有的</span><span>话</span><span>，您有没有感</span><span>觉</span><span>中国人更想知道客</span><span>观</span><span>的</span><span>历</span><span>史？我想了解您从</span><span>读</span><span>者的反</span><span>应</span><span>得到的感受。</span></p>\n<p><span>答：</span><span>不怕挨骂。因为我所写的，都是事实，有根据。依据</span><span>我所收到的</span><span>读</span><span>者来信反</span><span>馈</span><span>，</span><span>读过</span><span>我的</span><span>书</span><span>的</span><span>人</span><span>，基本上都</span><span>持有</span><span>赞赏</span><span>的</span><span>态</span><span>度，因</span><span>为</span><span>我的文字所</span><span>说</span><span>的是事</span><span>实</span><span>。而至于</span><span>骂</span><span>我是“</span><span>卖</span><span>国</span><span>贼</span><span>”的人，当然</span><span>也</span><span>有</span><span>。</span><span>但是</span><span>这</span><span>一</span><span>类</span><span>人往往是没有</span><span>读过</span><span>我</span><span>这</span><span>本</span><span>书</span><span>、</span><span>而</span><span>只是道听途</span><span>说</span><span>的。</span><span>是的，我感觉到：有许多的中国人，希望知道客观的历史。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（4）您了解到的</span><span>读</span><span>者大概多大</span><span>岁</span><span>，有什么</span><span>样</span><span>的背景？</span></p>\n<p>\n<span>答：据我所了解，我的</span><span>读</span><span>者以青年</span><span>为</span><span>主，也有不少是中年人。背景有影</span><span>视</span><span>明星、学院教授、青年学生、出版界人士、媒体人士等</span><span>，我没有做过详尽的调查，但据我所知基本是这样。</span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（5）您在</span><span>书</span><span>上写您写的是客</span><span>观</span><span>的史</span><span>实</span><span>。那么您</span><span>对这</span><span>史</span><span>实</span><span>有什么看法？</span></p>\n<p><span>答：</span><span>我写历史的基本态度是“多写事实，少谈看法”。而如果必须要我提供一个看法的话，那么我可以尝试高度总结如下：日本为什么侵华？主要原因在于以下两点：</span><span>1<span>、殖民主义。</span>2<span>、共产主义。前者是经济，后者是国防。依据我的理解，日本当年的两大主要诉求是：</span>1<span>、殖民。</span>2<span>、防共。而当时日本的具体做法，与中国当年的民族主义，发生了激烈的冲突。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（6）您</span><span>对现</span><span>在的中日关系，</span><span>还</span><span>有日本政治和外交有什么看法</span><span>吗</span><span>？</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n答：我33%的</span><span>时</span><span>间</span><span>用来上班、33%的</span><span>时</span><span>间</span><span>用来研究</span><span>历</span><span>史、33％的</span><span>时</span><span>间</span><span>用来</span><span>休息。我没有能力、也没有</span><span>兴</span><span>趣</span><span>对</span><span>现实</span><span>政治</span><span>发</span><span>表看法。</span><span>还请见谅。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（7）您与日本有什么关系？比如您的工作与日本有关，或者从小喜</span><span>欢</span><span>看日本漫画等。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n答：我和日本没有关系。我的工作内容和日本无关。我从小不喜</span><span>欢</span><span>日本漫画。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（8）关于您的背景。您</span><span>为</span><span>何什么</span><span>时</span><span>候开始那么</span><span>热爱历</span><span>史？您</span><span>现</span><span>在做什么工作（与</span><span>历</span><span>史完全没关系的</span><span>吗</span><span>？）您的大概的年</span><span>龄</span><span>（60后？70后？80后？）</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n答：我在</span><span>香港</span><span>一家美</span><span>资</span><span>移</span><span>动设备</span><span>及</span><span>电</span><span>脑</span><span>公司，从事法</span><span>务</span><span>工作，</span><span>工作内容</span><span>与</span><span>历</span><span>史完全无关。我是从大</span><span>约</span><span>十年前开始</span><span>对历</span><span>史</span><span>发生强烈兴趣</span><span>的。我生于<br />\n1979 年。</span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n </span></p>\n<p>\n<span>（9）下一个您在准</span><span>备</span><span>写的</span><span>题</span><span>目是什么？</span></p>\n<p>\n<span>答：2014年3月1日，我</span><span>刚刚</span><span>在香港出版了新</span><span>书</span><span>《从共和到内</span><span>战</span><span>：</span><span>见</span><span>证</span><span>北洋十七年》，探</span><span>讨</span><span>的是 1912年－1928年的中国内政，此</span><span>书</span><span>没有涉及日本</span><span>话题</span><span>。</span></p>\n<p>\n<span> </span><span>    <br />\n     <span>如果你有更多的问题，欢迎继续提问，谢谢。</span></span></p>\n<p>\n<span> </span></p>\n<p align=\"right\">\n<span>冯学荣</span><span>  2014<span>年</span>3<span>月</span>11<span>日</span>  <span>于</span>  <span>中国香港</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span> </span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/001rIEI0gy6HdSEQWDv59\"><img src=\"http://s10.sinaimg.cn/mw690/001rIEI0gy6HdSEQWDv59&#038;690\"></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/special/1265.gif\"> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://sina.allyes.com/main/adfclick?db=sina&#038;bid=204720,469641,474922&#038;cid=0,0,0&#038;sid=473458&#038;advid=358&#038;camid=37389&#038;show=ignore&#038;url=http://qing.blog.sina.com.cn/tag/%E5%86%99%E7%9C%9F\">青春就应该这样绽放</a>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://sina.allyes.com/main/adfclick?db=sina&#038;bid=204720,469645,474926&#038;cid=0,0,0&#038;sid=473464&#038;advid=358&#038;camid=37389&#038;show=ignore&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Funion.9173.com%2Fpub%3Fp%3D1%26u%3D1008\">游戏测试：三国时期谁是你最好的兄弟！！</a>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://sina.allyes.com/main/adfclick?db=sina&#038;bid=204720,469646,474927&#038;cid=0,0,0&#038;sid=473465&#038;advid=358&#038;camid=37389&#038;show=ignore&#038;url=http://qing.blog.sina.com.cn/tag/%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7\">你不得不信的星座秘密</a><img src=\"http://sina.allyes.com/main/adfclick?db=sina&#038;bid=204720,470173,475454&#038;cid=0,0,0&#038;sid=474001&#038;advid=358&#038;camid=37389&#038;show=ignore&#038;url=http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif?t=0\"></p>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/cdtimes./index.html?u=chinese\">中国数字时代亚马逊镜像</a>（墙内可直接点击）</p>\n","author":1004,"categories":[18270,18269,9203],"tags":[12025,9400,9826,8712]}